ugh glob patterns - correct.\n7. `im.service.ts` sendMessage: Redis incr is OUTS
IDE the transaction (line 131 after transaction on line 127) - correct per nestj
s.md.\n8. `im.service.ts` markAsRead: Redis set is OUTSIDE transaction - correct
.\n\nBut wait, `im.service.ts` `sendMessage` has a try/catch around the transact
